ld know about the game:</strong><br>-\tYou can pet the dog.<br>-\tThe game only saves when you die.<br>-\tEvery time you die, something changes.<br>-\tDying can be a good thing.<br>-\tA shotgun is a great ice breaker on a date.<br>-\tEach playthrough will be a new take on the game.<br>-\tYou can’t trust us.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613670/extras/d9340961d2d53ed2ec4eadd268f26aef.poster.avif?t=1749215314\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613670/extras/d9340961d2d53ed2ec4eadd268f26aef.webm?t=1749215314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613670/extras/d9340961d2d53ed2ec4eadd268f26aef.mp4?t=1749215314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>So come with us if you want to die.<br>- John & Maria<br>Professional Villains",
